cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically edge detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graph-based algorithms, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics). The use of neural networks for higher-level feature extraction suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another possible category. The paper also mentions parallelism, which could be related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
